      1 Remove dependency on problematic nas01 file server.  Currently it is used only for communicating changes between oasis-login and oasis, and that functionality will instead be moved to the shared filesystem now used for storage of repositories that&#39;s directly attached to the hypervisor of all the oasis* machines.

